                "title": "Minimum Wage Requirements",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "data": "The minimum wage is CZK 16,200 per month."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Individual Income Tax",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "The individual income tax ranges from 15% to 23%. Income tax is calculated according to progressive rates."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "table",
                        "data": [
                            {
                                "Gross Annual Income": "Up to CZK 1,701,168",
                                "Tax Rate (%)": "15%"
                            },
